      "subsections": {
        "Infectious": {
          "text": "Critical\nSepsis\nPNA\nwith respiratory failure\nPeritonitis\nMeningitis\nCavernous Sinus Thrombosis\nNecrotizing Fasciitis\nEmergent\nPNA\nPeritonsillar Abscess\nRetropharyngeal Abscess\nEpiglottitis\nEndocarditis\nPericarditis\nAppendicitis\nCholecystitis\nDiverticulitis\nIntra-abdominal abscess\nPyelonephritis\nTubo-ovarian abscess\nEncephalitis\nBrain abscess\nCellulitis\nAbscess\nMalaria\nNon-emergent\nViral syndrome\nOtitis Media\nSinusitis\nPharyngitis\nInfluenza\nTB\nUTI\nEpididymitis\nProstatitis",
