          "text": "Every 0.55°C increase in temperature should → increase HR by ~10BPM\nIf patient has relative bradycardia, consider:\nConcomitant medication\nDrug fever\nTyphoid Fever\nBrucellosis\nLeptospirosis\nIf patient has frank bradycardia, consider:\nRheumatic Fever\nLyme Disease\nViral Myocarditis\nEndocarditis",
